The '''Battle of Doljești''' was fought on 12 April 1457 and the '''Battle of Orbic''' was fought on 14 April 1457 between the forces of [[Ştefan cel Mare]] and the forces of [[Petru Aron]]. Ştefan cel Mare was aided by the Wallachians under [[Vlad III the Impaler]]. Ştefan's forces were victorious, and he was made Stephen III of Moldavia.

