{{Infobox airport | name = Bria Airport | IATA = BIV | ICAO = FEFR | type = Public | city-served = [[Bria, Central African Republic]] | location = | owner = | elevation-f = 1916 | elevation-m = | coordinates = {{coord|6|31|45|N|21|59|20|E|region:CF_type:airport|name=Bria Airport (Bria)|display=inline,title}} | pushpin_map = Central African Republic | pushpin_label = '''BIV''' | pushpin_map_caption = Location of Bria Airport in the Central African Republic | metric-rwy = y | r1-number = 14/32 | r1-length-f = | r1-length-m = 1722 | r1-surface = Dirt | footnotes = Source: Landings.com<ref name="Landings">[http://aerobaticsweb.org/cgi-bin/search_apt?FEFR Airport record for Bria Airport] at Landings.com. Retrieved 2013-08-25</ref> Google Maps<ref name="Google">{{Google maps|url=https://maps.google.com/maps?ht=en&z=13&t=k&q=6.52875,21.9886944444444+%28Bria+Airport%29|title=location of Bria Airport|accessdate=2013-08-25}}</ref> GCM<ref>{{GCM|BIV|Bria Airport}}</ref> }}
'''Bria Airport''' {{Airport codes|BIV|FEFR}} is an airport serving [[Bria, Central African Republic|Bria]], a town on the [[Kotto River]] in the [[Haute-Kotto]] prefecture of the [[Central African Republic]]. The airport is in the southern section of the town.
The Bria [[VHF omnidirectional range|VOR]] (Ident: '''IA''') is located on the field.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ourairports.com/navaids/IA/Bria_VOR_CF/|title=Bria VOR (IA) @ OurAirports|website=ourairports.com|access-date=2018-08-20}}</ref>
