'''Lambaréné Airport''' {{airport codes|LBQ|FOGR}} is an airport serving the city of [[Lambaréné]] in the [[Moyen-Ogooué Province]] of [[Gabon]]. The runway has and additional {{convert|380|m}} of unpaved overrun on the northeastern end.
The Lambarene [[non-directional beacon]] (Ident: '''LB''') is located southwest of the field.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://skyvector.com/?ll=-0.7048442,10.2428352&chart=301&zoom=1|title=SkyVector: Flight Planning / Aeronautical Charts|website=skyvector.com|access-date=2018-08-20}}</ref>
