{{Infobox diocese | jurisdiction = Diocese | name = Nha Trang | latin = Dioecesis Nhatrangensis | local = Giáo Phận Nha Trang | image = Mặt tiền Nhà thờ Núi.JPG | image_size = 230px | image_alt = | caption = Nha Trang Cathedral | coat = <!-- Coat of arms file name (excluding File: prefix) --> | coat_size = | coat_alt = | flag = <!-- Flag file name (excluding File: prefix) --> | flag_size = | flag_alt = <!---- Locations ----> | country = [[Vietnam]] | territory = | province = [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Huế|Huế]] | metropolitan = [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Huế|Huế]] | archdeaconries = | deaneries = | subdivisions = | coordinates = <!-- Use {{coord}} --> <!---- Statistics ----> | area_km2 = 9,486 | area_sqmi = <!-- Area in square miles, automatically converted --> | area_footnotes = | population = 1,786,000 | population_as_of = 2013 | catholics = 200,385 | catholics_percent = 11.2 | parishes = 90 | churches = <!-- Number of churches in the diocese --> | congregations = <!-- Number of congregations in the diocese --> | schools = <!-- Number of church supported schools in the diocese --> | members = <!-- Number of members in the diocese --> <!---- Information ----> | denomination = [[Roman Catholic]] | sui_iuris_church = [[Latin Church]] | rite = [[Roman Rite]] | established = {{unbulleted list| 1957 <small>(as Vicariate Apostolic of Nha Trang)</small>| 1960 <small>(as Diocese of Nha Trang)</small>| }} | cathedral = [[Christ the King Cathedral, Nha Trang|Christ the King in Nha Trang]] | cocathedral = | patron = <!-- Patron saint(s) of the diocese (or archdiocese) --> | patron_title = <!-- Use to override the default label "Patron saint" --> | priests = <!-- Number of priests in the diocese --> <!---- Current leadership ----> | pope = {{Incumbent pope}} <!-- DO NOT CHANGE. This will update the Popes Automatically as they change --> | patriarch = | major_archbishop = | bishop = [[Joseph Võ Đức Minh]] | bishop_title = <!-- Type of ordinary: i.e. Bishop or Archbishop. Default is Bishop --> | metro_archbishop = [[Joseph Nguyễn Chí Linh]] | coadjutor = | suffragans = <!-- List most senior first (usually reckoned by date of consecration); use | suffragan = for one --> | auxiliary_bishops = <!-- List most senior first (usually reckoned by date of consecration) --> | apostolic_admin = | vicar_general = | episcopal_vicar = | archdeacons = <!-- List most senior first (usually reckoned by date of first collation); use | archdeacon = for one--> | emeritus_bishops = <!---- Map ----> | map = | map_size = | map_alt = | map_caption = <!---- Website ----> | website = [http://giaophannhatrang.org/ giaophannhatrang.org] | footnotes = }} The '''diocese of Nha Trang''' ({{lang-la|Dioecesis Nhatrangensis|links=no}}) is a [[Roman Catholic]] diocese of [[Vietnam]]. The current bishop is [[Joseph Võ Đức Minh]], since December 4, 2009.
The creation of the diocese in present form was declared November 24, 1960.
The diocese covers an area of 9,486&nbsp;km², and is a [[suffragan diocese]] of the [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Huế|Archdiocese of Huế]].
By 2013, the diocese of Nha Trang had about 200,385 Catholics (11.2% of the population), 191 priests and 90 parishes.<ref>[http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dnhat.html Catholic Hierarchy Directory]</ref>
[[Christ the King Cathedral, Nha Trang|Christ the King Cathedral]] in [[Nha Trang]] has been assigned as the [[Cathedral]] of the [[diocese]].<ref>[http://www.gcatholic.org/churches/data/cathVN.htm#chk GCatholic.org]</ref>
