813 – 21 January 1820)'' # [[Geronimo do Barco]], [[Order of Friars Minor|OFM]] (21 January 1820 – 27 December 1831) # ''Sede vacante (27 December 1831 – 31 May 1845)'' # [[Patrício Xavier de Moura]] (31 May 1845 – 15 April 1859) # [[João Crisóstomo de Amorim Pessoa]] (8 June 1859 – 22 March 1861) # ''Sede vacante (22 March 1861'' ''– 25 September 1865)'' # [[José Luís Alves Feijó]] (25 September 1865 – 26 June 1871) # [[José Dias Correia de Carvalho]] (26 June 1871 – 9 August 1883) # [[Joaquim Augusto de Barros]] (27 March 1884 – 1 March 1904) # [[António Moutinho]] (14 November 1904 – 4 March 1909) # [[José Alves Martins]] (10 March 1910 – 15 November 1935) # [[Joaquim Rafael Maria d'Assunção Pitinho]], [[Order of Friars Minor|OFM]] (15 November 1935 – 5 May 1940) # [[Faustino Moreira dos Santos]], [[Congregation of the Holy Spirit|CSSp]] (28 January 1941 – 27 July 1955) # [[José Filípe do Carmo Colaço]] (28 March 1956 – 21 April 1975) # [[Paulino do Livramento Évora]], [[Congregation of the Holy Spirit|CSSp]] (21 April 1975 – 22 July 2009) # [[Arlindo Gomes Furtado]] (22 July 2009 – )
